  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, a lot of times you go to school, you don't know someone's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I mean, in USY, you know, everyone's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Let me tell you something about my son and my grandson.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the little one is not here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all I can tell you is in all what I went through, through the war, and since the liberation and all, these are the blessings that I thank God a hundred times a day.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My son was the easiest to raise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Thank God had never problems with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's not just because I say so now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was-- my neighbors and my friends always used to say, when there was-- they started to complain about their children, [LAUGHS] they used-- they used to say, you don't talk.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't have anything what to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He still is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He is--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He is-- well, I'll get to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He is the son and daughter-- the daughter that I almost had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Thank God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This kid?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This one?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This kid is, when we go someplace out, and he'll hold onto his zaide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And when I showed him one time a picture of somebody that I met in-- in Berlin, that we-- his uncle was a cantor, and he wanted me very badly to date him.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
